ProcedureHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: PROC COMPARE <option(s)>;
    BY <DESCENDING> variable-1 <...<DESCENDING> variable-n> <NOTSORTED>;  
    ID <DESCENDING> variable-1 <...<DESCENDING> variable-n> <NOTSORTED>;  
    VAR variable(s);  
    WITH variable(s);  

The COMPARE procedure compares the contents of two SAS data sets, selected variables 
in different data sets, or variables within the same data set.
